PinkHello https://pinkhello.me/posts/08-gradle%E5%A4%9A%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF%E5%8C%96/ -<h2 id="前言">前言</h2>
<p>Maven 冗余， Gradle 简单轻便
公司原有的 CI/CD 流程，借助 Maven 插件 build Docker Image,改为原生 Docker Runner 原始构建</p>
<h2 id="1多模块项目">1、多模块项目</h2>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">project<span style="color:#bbb">
