<p>Project/versions.gradle 可以统一版本管理</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-groovy" data-lang="groovy"><span style="color:#228b22">//start step
